  "markdown": "<!DOCTYPE html><html lang=\"en-US\" style=\"--screen-height: 100000px;\">\n\n<body class=\"page page-template-law-home-page\" id=\"fl_bp_3\">\n\n\n\n        <main id=\"main-content\" class=\"ability-corporate flw-general-main-content\">\n                \n            <div class=\"root\">\n                    <div class=\"general-hero\">\n    <section class=\"aem-default-hero hero main\">\n                <div class=\"general-hero-content main-content-focus\">\n            <div class=\"general-hero-content__breadcrumbs\">\n                <div class=\"row updated-breadcrumb-list\">\n                    <ol>\n                        <li>\n                <a href=\"https://www.findlaw.com/\">FindLaw </a>\n                <span class=\"breadcrumb-separator\" aria-hidden=\"true\">/</span>\n            </li>\n                                <li aria-current=\"page\">Learn About The Law </li>\n            </ol>\n\n                </div>\n            </div>\n            \n            <div class=\"general-hero-content-description\">\n                <h1 class=\"fl-h1-landing\">Learn About the Law</h1>\n                <p class=\"fl-text-lg\"></p><p>FindLaw provides free articles about state and federal laws. These resources can help you better understand your rights and the legal issues you may face. Our informational articles use an easy-to-read approach to cover many legal areas. Find our complete list of legal areas and state laws listed below.</p>\n<p></p>\n            </div>\n                            <div class=\"general-hero-content-image\">\n                    <img decoding=\"async\" src=\"https://www.findlaw.com/static/c/images/images/w_1200,c_limit,dpr_auto/f_auto,q_auto:eco/v1750684197/ability-law/wp-prod/general-components-hero-latl-banner_image_latl/general-components-hero-latl-banner_image_latl.jpg?_i=AA\" alt=\"\">\n                </div>\n                    </div>\n    </section>\n</div>\n\n\n            <div class=\"general-hero\">\n      